            "type": "code",
            "language": "text",
            "code": ">>> deg = np.arange(12.) * 30.\n>>> np.radians(deg)\narray([ 0.        ,  0.52359878,  1.04719755,  1.57079633,  2.0943951 ,\n        2.61799388,  3.14159265,  3.66519143,  4.1887902 ,  4.71238898,\n        5.23598776,  5.75958653])"
          },
          {
            "type": "code",
